POST <https://api.openai.com/v1/responses> - This is the single endpoint currently being used aris. which takes user query and searches through vector store.
1. internally retrieves top_k chunks 
2. returns which files in vectorstore it referenced.
3. frames response from top chunks and returns. 
Request Format :
```import OpenAI from "openai";

const openai = new OpenAI();

const response = await openai.responses.create({
    model: "gpt-4.1",
    input: "Tell me a three sentence bedtime story about a unicorn."
});

console.log(response);```
